  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\nDependant on closure of https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/pull/6508 before starting.\r\n\r\nFound during testing: https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/pull/6508#issuecomment-1213051052 (item 9)\r\n\r\nWhen pasting text from a website that has a defined background color then it is being included in the message box.\r\n\r\nNote: the background is removed on sending\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\nPaste text from website into message box\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/50769329/184619951-2608890a-b5f5-436a-af33-235acc1bab51.png)\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/50769329/184620064-d2a903ce-2762-43a7-8bb0-1875ba9d6b87.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nBackground is removed.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nBackground is included\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status desktop version: Master (12/Aug)\r\n- Operating System: Mac\r\n\r\n",
